==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[specific]] [[leaf]] [[area]]}}

#{{botany}} a measure of leaf [[thickness]], calculated by dividing the [[area]] of a portion of a leaf by the dry [[weight]] of that same portion of leaf.

